# Local config for scripts/sync-agent-comms.{sh,ps1}.
#
# Copy this file to .sync-config (which is gitignored) and fill in
# the AGENT_COMMS_REMOTE path on YOUR machine. The sync script reads
# from .sync-config so the script itself stays free of personal paths.

# Path to the OTHER checkout's copy of the agent-comms doc.
# Example (Windows): C:\Users\<you>\<other-repo>\docs\plans\2026-05-21-project-starter-recommendations.md
# Example (Mac):     /Users/<you>/<other-repo>/docs/plans/2026-05-21-project-starter-recommendations.md
AGENT_COMMS_REMOTE=
